msgctxt "#30817"
msgid "Verbose Logging"
msgstr "Podrobné logovanie"

msgctxt "#30917"
msgid "Log API responses and stream details to the Kodi log. Useful for diagnosing playback issues. Leave off for normal use - the log gets noisy."
msgstr "Zapisuje odpovede API a detaily streamu do Kodi logu. Užitočné pri diagnostike problémov s prehrávaním. Pre bežné používanie nechajte vypnuté - log sa stáva zahltený."

msgctxt "#30818"
msgid "[COLOR yellow]Master Lock is enabled — adult content stays hidden[/COLOR]"
msgstr "[COLOR yellow]Master Lock je zapnutý — kanály pre dospelých sú skryté[/COLOR]"

msgctxt "#30918"
msgid "Kodi's Master Lock is on, so the addon hides all adult channels regardless of the toggle below. Disable Master Lock in System settings if you want full control via this addon."
msgstr "Kodi Master Lock je zapnutý, doplnok preto skrýva všetky kanály pre dospelých bez ohľadu na prepínač nižšie. Vypnite Master Lock v systémových nastaveniach, ak chcete plnú kontrolu cez tento doplnok."

msgctxt "#30717"
msgid "Sweet.TV details"
msgstr "Sweet.TV detaily"

msgctxt "#30718"
msgid "Enter PIN to unlock adult content"
msgstr "Zadajte PIN pre odomknutie obsahu pre dospelých"

msgctxt "#30719"
msgid "PVR IPTV Simple Client is not installed. Install it from the Kodi addon repository first."
msgstr "PVR IPTV Simple Client nie je nainštalovaný. Najprv ho nainštalujte z repozitára doplnkov Kodi."

msgctxt "#30720"
msgid "PVR IPTV Simple Client has not been configured yet. Its settings will open now - close them, then run this action again."
msgstr "PVR IPTV Simple Client ešte nebol nakonfigurovaný. Otvoria sa jeho nastavenia - zatvorte ich a spustite túto akciu znova."

msgctxt "#30721"
msgid "PVR IPTV Simple Client configured. Channels and EPG should appear in the TV section after a moment."
msgstr "PVR IPTV Simple Client nakonfigurovaný. Kanály a EPG by sa mali za chvíľu objaviť v sekcii TV."

msgctxt "#30722"
msgid "All Channels"
msgstr "Všetky kanály"

msgctxt "#30723"
msgid "Move Up"
msgstr "Posunúť hore"

msgctxt "#30724"
msgid "Move Down"
msgstr "Posunúť dole"

msgctxt "#30725"
msgid "This will install IPTV Manager and PVR IPTV Simple Client (if missing), refresh the channel list, and configure everything to plug into Kodi's TV section. Continue?"
msgstr "Toto nainštaluje IPTV Manager a PVR IPTV Simple Client (ak chýbajú), obnoví zoznam kanálov a všetko nakonfiguruje pre integráciu s Kodi sekciou TV. Pokračovať?"

msgctxt "#30726"
msgid "Installing dependencies..."
msgstr "Inštalujem závislosti..."

msgctxt "#30727"
msgid "Fetching channels and EPG..."
msgstr "Načítavam kanály a EPG..."

msgctxt "#30728"
msgid "Configuring PVR Simple Client..."
msgstr "Konfigurujem PVR Simple Client..."

msgctxt "#30729"
msgid "Failed to install {addon}. Try installing it manually from the Kodi addon repository, then run this action again."
msgstr "Inštalácia {addon} zlyhala. Skúste ho nainštalovať ručne z repozitára doplnkov Kodi a spustite túto akciu znova."

msgctxt "#30730"
msgid "IPTV Manager did not produce the channel list within the timeout. Open IPTV Manager settings and try Force Refresh manually, then run Configure PVR Simple Client."
msgstr "IPTV Manager nevytvoril zoznam kanálov v stanovenom čase. Otvorte nastavenia IPTV Managera a skúste Force Refresh ručne, potom spustite Konfigurovať PVR Simple Client."

msgctxt "#30837"
msgid "Setup PVR Integration"
msgstr "Nastaviť PVR integráciu"

msgctxt "#30937"
msgid "One-shot full setup: installs IPTV Manager and PVR IPTV Simple Client (if missing), triggers an IPTV Manager refresh, and configures PVR Simple Client to read sweet.tv channels and EPG. Run this on a fresh install."
msgstr "Plné nastavenie jedným klikom: nainštaluje IPTV Manager a PVR IPTV Simple Client (ak chýbajú), spustí obnovu IPTV Managera a nakonfiguruje PVR Simple Client na čítanie sweet.tv kanálov a EPG. Spustite po čerstvej inštalácii."

msgctxt "#30836"
msgid "Configure PVR IPTV Simple Client"
msgstr "Konfigurovať PVR IPTV Simple Client"

msgctxt "#30936"
msgid "One-click setup: points PVR IPTV Simple Client at the IPTV Manager M3U/EPG files, enables catchup, and renames the instance to Sweet.TV. Run this once after installing the addon."
msgstr "Inštalácia jedným klikom: nasmeruje PVR IPTV Simple Client na M3U/EPG súbory IPTV Managera, zapne catchup a premenuje inštanciu na Sweet.TV. Spustite raz po inštalácii doplnku."

msgctxt "#30819"
msgid "Adult Content PIN"
msgstr "PIN pre obsah pre dospelých"

msgctxt "#30919"
msgid "Optional PIN to gate adult content. If set, you'll be asked for it once per Kodi session before adult channels are shown. If left empty, adult channels are shown without any prompt."
msgstr "Nepovinný PIN pre zamknutie obsahu pre dospelých. Ak je nastavený, raz za reláciu Kodi sa naň spýta pred zobrazením kanálov pre dospelých. Ak je prázdny, kanály pre dospelých sa zobrazia bez akejkoľvek výzvy."

